<section class="why-carver section">
  <div class="container text-center">
    <p class="eyebrow">LET US FIGHT FOR YOU</p>
    <h2>Criminal Law Firm in Springfield MO</h2>
    
    <div class="why-grid">
      <div class="why-item">
        <h3>VIGOROUSLY FIGHT THE PROSECUTION'S CASE</h3>
        <p>We leave no stone unturned in examining the evidence and challenging the government's narrative.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-item">
        <h3>DEFEND YOUR CONSTITUTIONAL RIGHTS</h3>
        <p>Your rights are our priority. We ensure every legal protection is enforced throughout your case.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-item">
        <h3>SECURE THE MOST OPTIMAL OUTCOME FOR YOU</h3>
        <p>Whether through trial or negotiation, we strive for the best possible result for your future.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .why-carver { background: var(--color-primary); color: #fff; padding: 6rem 0; }
  .text-center { text-align: center; }
  .eyebrow { color: var(--color-accent); font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.15em; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .why-carver h2 { color: #fff; font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 4rem; }

  .why-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 4rem;
  }

  .why-item h3 { color: #fff; font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.4; }
  .why-item p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); }
</style>
